{"tid":2423822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰晤士高等教育：段崇智膺風雲人物 堅定為校園學生挺身而出","createTime":"2021-02-26T06:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:06:02.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1ec4b7094ddd9bb7edfe3c5dcba0f2bba02872","tid":2423822,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:57:17.000Z","msg":"泰晤士高等教育（Times Higher Education）今日（17日）公布2019年度全球高等教育風雲人物，香港中文大學校長段崇智榜上有名。評選的記者描述，香港所有大學領袖都被捲入示威風波，但沒太多像段崇智般堅定為他的校園及學生挺身而出。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士高等教育》記者評選出11名對2019年高等教育界有影響力的學者或行政人員，其中關於段崇智的篇幅提到，新聞相片顯示段崇智11月中時，冒着危險到猶如戰場的中大校園，試圖使示威者與警方達成和平協議。衝突期間，警方透過大聲公呼籲「段校長及大學職員請立即離開，現在不是談判或者對話的時間」，之後就向段崇智的方向發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士高等教育》記者形容，未發生此事前，段崇智已經接觸不同學生，聆聽他們的不滿，同時呼籲停止暴力，即使被官方人士批評，仍然如一。該記者認為，中大是近日暴力事件中被破壞得最嚴重的兩間學校之一，段崇智來年主要的挑戰不是課室或實驗室，而是重建校園。"},{"pid":"f0ef3af330643c24e55b62f45ab3a49f27f994bd","tid":2423822,"uid":388108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042192116463010f760fa8ed8fa0884e101dd73c","tid":2423822,"uid":313334,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"段爸段爸換來一巴一巴"},{"pid":"b484c50758081f5c3848430e3aad336a539ab77e","tid":2423822,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042192116463010f760fa8ed8fa0884e101dd73c","tid":2423822,"uid":313334,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"段爸段爸換來一巴一巴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:59:09.000Z","msg":"押韻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b314396e992bbee81e75f668d15cea2e45fea5d","tid":2423822,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"奶到雪雪聲都可以做風雲人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b8d764b258dd2cf615ad2d818db0794cae56d6","tid":2423822,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"今日（17日）?"},{"pid":"e07e11091e71e35f84afb82f3b92d28833dc53ee","tid":2423822,"uid":261819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"唔撚係咁on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不嬲中大人都叫佢段狗<br />\n<br />\n理大恐襲果幾個中學校長好過佢唔知幾多啦"},{"pid":"c856a73d7b367e191c50c3c051f68636e05f58d2","tid":2423822,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"Thames 先係泰晤士......"},{"pid":"1bf373a7c451c5ac1a57cbfa08324dbb58135050","tid":2423822,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b8d764b258dd2cf615ad2d818db0794cae56d6","tid":2423822,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"今日（17日）?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea259d466cdbb32c862a3192d09586f13bb2c150","tid":2423822,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3K3v9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3K3v9n.jpg&h=98f7c577&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebc7013ff6e00fbeb61b486a9f9c2a3a86a508a2","tid":2423822,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191217/s00001/1576587937393/%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E8%86%BA%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9-%E8%A9%95%E9%81%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E5%A0%85%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%BA%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%BA%E8%BA%AB%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191217%2Fs00001%2F1576587937393%2F%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B4%2